In the INTEREST OF C.S., Minor Child, J.S., Father, Appellant, C.S., Mother, Appellant. No. 19-0343 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 19, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and father separately appeal the termination of their parental rights to their minor child. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
